            <h4>Brief introduction</h4>

            <p>
                Drugs are given to patients for their beneficial effects on the body, but they can also cause
                side-effects. "GenderedReactions" provides information to the public about drug side-effects
                that are gender differentiated to create a greater awareness of variations between the two sexes.
            </p>

            <p>
                Note that this website is in 'beta' and under going further development. Please contact us with
